author: Andrew O'Reilly
title: Coronavirus strikes homeless in Los Angeles and Seattle as local officials grapple with outbreak
description: The first cases of COVID-19 have been reported among the homeless in Los Angeles and Seattle – adding to the already heightened concerns of local officials that the contagion could spread like wildfire through an extremely vulnerable segment of the population.
